ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f55e894903c7d8a715d63bb97e5d064d1edb44d8","tid":776138,"uid":59240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffbcd8216576735001f3633e3de78d9a688cc9a0","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"19b965b31840220340c0bb97b293fcbfd1f4b179","tid":776138,"uid":59240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"我依家同你都差唔多，每日都天光先訓到<br />\n都會諗翻起以前點解咁做點解會咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T20:51:18.000Z","msg":"人最大既煩惱就係記性太好<br />\n如果每朝訓醒都係一個新既開始，咁你話幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T20:53:17.000Z","msg":"記性太好真係好麻煩，好事記得當然好但唔好嘅事都會一齊記埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:04:47.000Z","msg":"但係除左記住之外，已經無野可以做到喇<br />\n<br />\n5點喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊試下訓啦"},{"pid":"8dc7b7164fe1fc67672e4d0ec8679d01806f978d","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dade3b53b9ce313391596669c230006d05d5b473","tid":776138,"uid":25300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:04:00.000Z","msg":"一年前<br />\n換了工作地方的我，和回復單身的她開始更多見面<br />\n<br />\n當你水泡 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:07:04.000Z","msg":"sad but true"},{"pid":"ebbbe02e37beefab644c6eebb8110350f3afbce4","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"仲要落幾耐雨<br />\n<br />\n我已經不可以 跟你做朋友<br />\n連人生 都迷失<br />\n努力愛一個人 都不夠<br />\n一時的享受 能熱暖多久<br />\n<br />\n最美好的一切 請你別硏究<br />\n誰值得 不值得<br />\n愛你不需理由 我卻知<br />\n錯過後哪可回頭<br />\n<br />\n曾聽說雨天總要放手 總要分手<br />\n曾跟你約定下個淡季 浪漫旅遊<br />\n明日看雨點灑到滿天 總會掛念<br />\n我會隱藏我淚線"},{"pid":"47e32fbeb89ccd9d45678eed8933458b5080bd4c","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"能不能繼續 對我哭 對我笑 對我好<br />\n繼續讓我 為你想 為你瘋 陪你老<br />\n你好不好 我好想知道<br />\n別急著把我的愛丟掉<br />\n<br />\n我只需要你在身邊 陪我吵 陪我鬧<br />\n別用離開教我 失去的人最重要<br />\n別說 你曾經愛過我<br />\n讓我們回到那一秒<br />\n你，好不好？"},{"pid":"99d84e880392406d160d470efbb16b0fb5253b03","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"好想搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1c1d499a3f4bc1491326e18f5edf7c7478092f","tid":776138,"uid":93463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<br />\n不捨得 捨不得 沒有什麼非誰不可<br />\n就讓自己慢慢成長<br />\n慢慢放下"},{"pid":"23bf2f48a9e7a283718c202c1f61fe54aeb07eb1","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a1c1d499a3f4bc1491326e18f5edf7c7478092f","tid":776138,"uid":93463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<br />\n不捨得 捨不得 沒有什麼非誰不可<br />\n就讓自己慢慢成長<br />\n慢慢放下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"人生最難的一課<br />\n就是學習接受失去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不論親人，朋友， 寵物<br />\n現在想起都會心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf9930167d6cd149d1b341dd7dc1cec6c904c2a","tid":776138,"uid":165824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"下次三思而後行 <br />\n有幾愛都唔好比佢知<br />\n下次會更好！忘記她！"},{"pid":"1a8c9c2c65707847f87506d8b3aa85197a114408","tid":776138,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf9930167d6cd149d1b341dd7dc1cec6c904c2a","tid":776138,"uid":165824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"下次三思而後行 <br />\n有幾愛都唔好比佢知<br />\n下次會更好！忘記她！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"我知道了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor